reviewText: This is expensive and has No English subtitles.

THIS PRICETag is super overpriced. Why anyone would spend 115 dollars for it's release seems to me being a ripoff. Unless they reportedly do 50 episodes and each episode is 2.89? I would give it 5 stars because I love this show and it's better than SAO it actually was written as a manga first. (It's more fun less dark.) BUT THE Price.
